title: Join us in Senpai Club!
body:
Hey Summoners!

We're looking for chill, casual people to just hit up norms/ARAMS and Overwatch if you have it :)

Feel free to click the discord link and say hello!

replies.body: Better change the server permissions because apparently anyone has the ability to move people between servers
Ill be home in 2 hours if you guys are still down :)
